# Notification System

## Overview

A React-based Notification System developed as part of the Afford Medical Technologies evaluation.

## Features

* Notification API Integration
* Authentication using Bearer Token
* Notification Filtering
* Pagination
* Priority Inbox
* Viewed/Unviewed Notification Tracking
* React Router Navigation
* Logging Middleware

## Project Structure

23BQ1A1248

* logging-middleware/
* notification_app/
* notification_system_design.md

## Technologies Used

### Frontend

* React
* Vite
* JavaScript
* React Router

### Middleware

* Node.js
* Axios

## How to Run

### Frontend

```bash
cd notification_app
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Middleware

```bash
cd logging-middleware
npm install
node auth.js
```

